Day 1: Set up FastAPI backend with SQLite database and inventory APIs. Verified functionality via Swagger UI and pushed to GitHub.

### Day 2
- Implemented Orders API using FastAPI
- Created order placement functionality with database persistence
- Linked orders with inventory to automatically reduce stock on order creation
- Added validation for insufficient inventory and missing items
- Tested complete supply chain flow using Swagger UI
- Verified inventory updates after successful order placement
